original: intros d h h' t lli llt d' m H. unfold is_request_vote_reply. destruct (Nat.ltb t (currentTerm d)) eqn:Hltb. - simpl in H. inversion H; subst. exists (currentTerm d), false. reflexivity. - remember (advanceCurrentTerm d t) as adv. remember ((if leaderId adv then false else true) && moreUpToDate llt lli (maxTerm (log adv)) (maxIndex (log adv))) as cond. destruct cond. + simpl in H. inversion H; subst. exists t, true. reflexivity. + simpl in H. inversion H; subst. exists t, false. reflexivity.
